a rel="noopener" target="_blank" href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/tag/wall-of-chefs/"><em>Wall of Chefs</em> chef</a> â€” to find out his tips and tricks for making the best rice ever, including his secret fail-safe method. Read on for rice 101.</p><div class="ad-wrapper article-ad-paragraph"><span class="ad-label">ADVERTISEMENT</span><div class="ad-slot article-ad-paragraph-wrapper adunitContainer"><div class="adBox" id="article-ad-1"></div></div></div>
<p>Related: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.foodnetwork.ca/article/delectable-rice-recipes/">7 Delectable Rice Recipes to Enjoy</a></p>
